    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#39;m on the tail end of a 31(!) day long cold-turned-sinus infection, so I feel your pain. I&#39;ve almost forgotten what it&#39;s like to wake up healthy! </p>
<p>Have you tried using nasal irrigation (Neti pot)? I was always skeptical, especially hearing about how someone in the states contracted a brain eating amoeba from using unfiltered water, but I was desperate for anything. And it totally helped! It moistens the sinuses and helps drain all the crap that&#39;s stuck up there. </p>
<p>Eating raw garlic also helps, but it is truly revolting. üôÇ</p>
